file: crates/ctx-cage/tests/bwrap_discover.rs
purpose: Integration tests for `discover_crate_dirs`, verifying correct discovery of `src`/`tests` dirs and clear error when `crates/` is absent.
invariants:
  - Each test creates and removes its own tempdir; no shared state beyond the atomic counter.
external_deps:
  - ctx_cage::bwrap: function under test.
  - ctx_cage::error::CageError: used as the error type for test return values.
functions: